img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3925a882488ab26cfabd1f0969fc4ef847ae4a0c","tid":1917852,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e589bd3b37fd5b7e3c2f929d17fff22647c3aba8","tid":1917852,"uid":92467,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T18:03:13.000Z","msg":"熱狗會追擊泛民先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T00:51:11.000Z","msg":"狗改不了吃⋯"},{"pid":"8ccd06a6c4eaf821e2b543b8554d2a6c4d5f12dc","tid":1917852,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"05ce15ceca645f0fd947235dd14dff0981cf40eb","tid":1917852,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T00:50:07.000Z","msg":"白票五毛黨又出動，保皇狗多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:12:37.000Z","msg":"轉貼兼勸諫啫！咁都被人話五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只可以講幾唔妥教主同游b都好，兩位上屆4萬幾票唔好睇小，唔好白白浪費。呢個時候鬥氣重要定選票重要，泛民黃絲應該識諗啦<br />\n<br />\n昨晚聽踩場，我而家先知平時個d民間記者會原來係議員助理蒙面扮發言人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296964408e93ffe34eab8e80028d03033b70e769","tid":1917852,"uid":261037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:14:48.000Z","msg":"又係熱狗論"},{"pid":"9bb6253ed6507b6a158ce2eddb04072047720ad3","tid":1917852,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"296964408e93ffe34eab8e80028d03033b70e769","tid":1917852,"uid":261037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:14:48.000Z","msg":"又係熱狗論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T01:32:01.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw我只係食花生，不作任何爭論"},{"pid":"e8a00f0a1daec8dd2f9d96c3cd4c16a8d244b5cd","tid":1917852,"uid":271211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"諗起進擊的巨人嘅最新一話<br />\n不論艾爾迪亞一方 定係馬萊一方<br />\n都有重要嘅人被對方殺左<br />\n但雙方為左[阻止艾倫]<br />\n呢個共同目標而選擇合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙方嘅心裏面條刺冇消失到<br />\n但佢地都選擇暫時放下分歧<br />\n如果泛民 本土 熱狗等<br />\n各方面都可以做到咁就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad5ed2719c7c77ed0a5bdd589e867679d9e8397","tid":1917852,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:16:42.000Z","msg":"Lak Lak Chin<br />\n1時間 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n如果採用好似2016年的棄選制，<br />\n我幾乎肯定，如果即使現任議員的民調低，佢一定不肯棄選。<br />\n<br />\n而他的基本盤係死忠鐵票，唔會輕易轉俾其他的候選人<br />\n<br />\n梁耀忠雖然好多人都叫佢退休，但其實佢地區的基本盤好硬淨，果D票唔會輕易轉俾人。馮檢基亦是相同的例子"},{"pid":"d15f200bd7dac9f401aa36059756a1e03979572f","tid":1917852,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46471430e9224a8f2db4ddd6e854ff919578fe78","tid":1917852,"uid":158888,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T18:03:40.000Z","msg":"可唔可以有共識<br />\n無論初選結果係點都要支持<br />\n同埋就算唔初選都要協調<br />\n我地一票不能少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"呢個唔止係共職嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n如果你要含嘅候選人不斷攻擊、侮辱你欣賞嘅議員，唔係個個都含得落<br />\n<br />\n呢個係有先例嘅事嚟"},{"pid":"1fd5f3a58fe0a35f0d02f4ede4ff2eb546f07bbd","tid":1917852,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ad5ed2719c7c77ed0a5bdd589e867679d9e8397","tid":1917852,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:16:42.000Z","msg":"Lak Lak Chin<br />\n1時間 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n如果採用好似